GET BY ID ==> http://localhost:8080/mycart/item/ITEM123
GET BY CATEGORY ==> http://localhost:8080/mycart/items/CAT001?includeSpecial=true
GET BY CATEGORY ID==>http://localhost:8080/category/cat1
POST NEW ITEM ==> http://localhost:8080/additem
POST NEW ITEM IN BULK ==> http://localhost:8080/mycart/bulk/items
POST NEW CATEGORY ==> http://localhost:8080/category/add
UPDATE THE VALUES ==> http://localhost:8080/mycart/item/{itemId}

